This guide will help you integrate Stripe Connect payments and teach you how to process proper commissions for each payment.

## Requirements

To follow this tutorial, you should be familiar with the Stripe API and the Stripe Dashboard.
You need to have access to the Partner Portal. Before you start, make sure that:

* you have Stripe configured correctly as explained in [Integrating Stripe](/developer-guide/payments/integrating-stripe)
* you understand GraphQL mutations and how you can process payments with them: [Processing Payments with GraphQL Mutations](/developer-guide/payments/processing-payments-graphql-mutations)

## Steps

1. Create Merchant Account
2. Automate payment transfers
3. Create manual payment transfers with mutations
4. Fetch transfers list
5. Configure automated payment fees
